originalText.text: I'm always looking for a healthy and delicious snack to take to work or to eat at home on the weekend. Came across hummustir, organic hummus dip/spread recently in Walmart and was so impressed by the simple ingredients and low calories, so I bought it! Then I gave it a good stir and dipped my pretzels into it.... absolutely delicious and so so smooth! So impressed.

originalText.text: Loved it.  You have to follow the directions and shake the container with the chickpea part of the hummus first. The tahini does separate, which it does in all containers as that is the nature of tahini you just have to stir it well first then add the tahini and stir well again. No lumps, tasted delicious.

originalText.text: The mix had separated completely and was hard to get out of the container. Then the two mixed together would not mix at all. Lots of stirring and still left big lumps. Will not buy again.
